## Authentication & Authorization | Bcrypt | JWT

    user ko profile dene se pahle ye check karna hota hai ke user hai kaun

    Authorized to perform some tasks which are only allowed to be executed by the admin

    server har baar bhool jata hai ki aap kaun ho, ab kyuki server bhool jaata hai aap kaun ho to har baar wo har kaam ke I iye aapse puchhega aap kaun ho

### sabse pahle humein kuchh cheejein seekhni hai a lag a lag

    i) cookie kaise set karte hai
    ii) bcrypt kaise use karte hai for password encrytption and decryption
    iii) jwt kya hai and jwt mein data kaise store karein and baahar nikaaleio

Install the JWT bcrypt command

```javascript
npm i jsonwebtoken bcrypt
```
